%% 4.1 后台查看用户列表（脱敏 → 角色校验 → 完整需留痕）
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin(浏览器)
    participant P as admin/users/page.tsx (Server)
    participant DB as Prisma/Neon
    participant T as users-table.tsx (Client)
    participant R as /admin/users/[id]/reveal-email
    participant L as PiiAuditLog

    A->>P: 访问 /admin/users
    P->>P: verifyToken + 角色门禁(仅 admin/super_admin)
    P->>DB: findMany(users, select 必要字段)
    DB-->>P: users[]
    P->>P: 逐条 maskEmail() + profileCompleteness()
    P-->>T: 下发 { emailMasked, completeness, roleViewer }
    T->>A: 渲染脱敏列表 + 完整度列
    A->>T: 点击某行"显示邮箱"
    T->>R: POST { id, purpose }
    R->>R: checkAdmin(role)
    R->>L: 写审计(actor,target,field=email)
    R->>DB: findUnique(email)
    DB-->>R: email(明文)
    R-->>T: { email: 明文 }
    T->>A: 就地展示完整邮箱（仅本次）
    Note over R,L: 非 admin 角色 → 403 拒绝，不返回明文

%% 4.2 小程序用户 web 补全邮箱（提交 → 设 emailVerified → 触发发分幂等）
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户(小程序→web)
    participant F as complete-profile-form.tsx
    participant API as /api/user/profile
    participant DB as Prisma/Neon
    participant G as grantRegisterGiftIfNeeded
    participant M as UserMilestone / CreditLot

    U->>F: 打开 /account/complete-profile
    F->>U: 展示表单 + "数据出境单独同意"勾选
    U->>F: 填 email/公司/国家/密码 + 勾选同意
    F->>API: POST { email, ..., dataCrossBorderConsent:true }
    API->>API: verifyToken(本人) + completeProfileSchema 校验
    API->>DB: update(userId, { email, companyName, country, passwordHash?, emailVerified:true, emailPending:false })
    API->>G: grantRegisterGiftIfNeeded(userId)
    G->>M: 查 UserMilestone(register_gift)
    alt 已存在（重复提交）
        M-->>G: 已发 → granted:false
    else 首次
        G->>M: 建 Milestone + CreditLot(gift) + CreditTransaction + credits+=
        M-->>G: granted:true, amount
    end
    G-->>API: { granted, amount }
    API-->>F: 200 { emailVerified:true, emailPending:false, credits }
    F->>U: 提示"资料已补全，积分已发放(如有)"

%% 4.3 管理员手动重置密码 + 站内信通知（0-4）
sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as 管理员
    participant UI as users-table.tsx (重置弹窗)
    participant API as /admin/reset-user-password
    participant DB as Prisma/Neon
    participant N as createInAppNotification
    participant NB as Notification 模型

    Admin->>UI: 点击"重置密码" → 输入新密码
    UI->>API: POST { userId, newPassword }
    API->>API: checkAdmin(role)
    API->>DB: update(userId, { passwordHash: bcrypt(newPassword) })
    API->>N: createInAppNotification({ userId, type:"password_reset", title, body, link })
    N->>NB: insert Notification
    NB-->>N: ok
    N-->>API: notified:true
    API-->>UI: 200 { notified:true }
    UI->>Admin: 提示"已重置并通知用户(站内信)"
    Note over API,N: 不发送邮件；订阅消息为 stub
